{"tid":425980,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【超越大時代】散戶黃生：向32000進發！遲早創新高","createTime":"2017-10-06T08:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T04:41:34.000Z","uid":24660,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbbfa11aabc34495e727089c526ca32afd703c8","tid":425980,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171006/large/1507266632_9e34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171006%2Flarge%2F1507266632_9e34.jpg&h=f7223ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n散戶黃先生笑著說今早因購入內房股而有收獲。<br />\n<br />\n今早恒指一度升穿28588大時代高位，一眾散戶都緊貼大市走勢，有賺亦有人蝕。散戶黃先生就笑着表示「多少有啦」，賺了多少就口密不透露，但表示買入了富力地產（2777），並認定目標之後會以買內地地產股和科技股騰訊為主。<span style=\"color: red;\">他又看好大市，認為大市遲早會創歷史新高，堅定指「30000向32000進發啦！」。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，有散戶則淡定指「等緊賺」，陳小姐說這兩天升得太急，要等大市回一回才會再入市，而她則認為大市應該會升至29,000點，並指會購入科技股，因為她認為將來都是科技股的世界。<br />\n<br />\n有人歡喜，亦有散戶心驚驚。面對恒指升穿大時代高位，林先生說：「唔夠膽啊！」，所以今早沒有因為股市上升而有所收獲，並指今早一直在排隊，之後會主攻買一些落後的股份，他看好華南城（1668）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171006/57297653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171006%2F57297653&d=RkDpb%2Fugp%2FKDARkKXTmhTttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ae21ce53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171006%2F57297653&h=c65ab9e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171006/57297653</a>"},{"pid":"112bff21bd19adaa250a2e9e99d2078a3a192b15","tid":425980,"uid":13718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資金準備買熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d89a7cda350e0840e4cd3bc8f85a2a9b2652d14","tid":425980,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺會30000點"},{"pid":"ce05432be84e577360ce245aefd13ffa278c3b06","tid":425980,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資金準備買熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係會三萬，唔講笑<br />\n不過下年將會開始熊市，狂歡埋呢幾個月好喇"},{"pid":"ad6787c4135b821eaef519a32b6619e03ebe7a3b","tid":425980,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"當老散全面進場之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46dc99644e3978fcdd9951b06299578c42d8a769","tid":425980,"uid":21708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"無咁快熊，等班廢老入曬閘先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a52ca731bf1ae5b3ef1a7ce73c3a29f957448fb","tid":425980,"uid":134969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"3萬就緊 但10月應該會整固下 12月1月相信會係牛3大時代"},{"pid":"c4f6ac269d3f446badac8a02f999fbd690a3fcf7","tid":425980,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3萬就緊 但10月應該會整固下 12月1月相信會係牛3大時代</blockquote><br />\n起碼下年啦"},{"pid":"37b4d0a24098f78f00c9195b8f9e9cf1b1b0eb68","tid":425980,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no